Salesforce.com Inc Completes Acquisition of ExactTarget
Friday, 12 Jul 2013 09:20am EDT
Salesforce.com Inc announced it has completed its acquisition of ExactTarget, a cloud marketing platform used by more than 6,000 companies including Coca-Cola, Gap and Nike. Salesforce.com's acquisition of ExactTarget furthers its mission of being the CRM platform-one that enables companies to transform how they connect with their customers across sales, service and marketing. By combining ExactTarget's digital marketing capabilities with salesforce.com's sales, service and social marketing solutions, salesforce.com will create a world-class marketing platform across email, social, mobile and the web.Â 
